because you care about me.


14
0:0:45,789 --> 0:0:50,54
Yeah, that's why I did it.


15
0:0:50,54 --> 0:0:52,303
All right.


16
0:0:52,303 --> 0:0:54,392
Here we go.


17
0:0:54,392 --> 0:1:6,401
