everybody left an hour ago.


20
0:1:12,418 --> 0:1:18,2
Surprise!


21
0:1:18,2 --> 0:1:21,359
Okay, Leonard.
I am at your birthday party.


22
0:1:21,359 --> 0:1:25,428
I don't know where you are,
dude, but it's really kick-ass!


23
0:1:25,428 --> 0:1:30,417
Everyone is very, very drunk and...


24
