That's my friend Carol.


26
0:1:36,951 --> 0:1:40,144
Remind me,
I gotta introduce her to Howard.


27
0:1:40,144 --> 0:1:45,694
Oh, sweet Krishna,
shake that rupee maker!


28
0:1:45,694 --> 0:1:48,42
I'm so sorry you didn't get your party.


29
0:1:48,42 --> 0:1:51,872
It's okay.


30
